name: INSIDE Air France La Premiere! The PERFECT FIRST CLASS Cabin?
description:
In this video, you’ll go inside La Premiere, which is Air France’s most exclusive First Class experience. It’s available on their most premium routes onboard some 777-300’s  (and, eventually, some A350’s). 

You’ll get a sense for the Air France First Class experience, including the secret Air France First Class lounge, the Air France First Class seat, the Air France First Class food, as well as the Inflight Entertainment.

But, perhaps best of all, you’ll get a feel for what the ultimate in inflight service is. Air France First Class service is a step above just about anything you can experience in the sky with any other airline.

Watch this video to decide for yourself whether a flight like this should be on your list!
